		{
			"identifier": "MovingPlatform",
			"uid": 4251,
			"tags": [],
			"exportToToc": false,
			"allowOutOfBounds": true,
			"doc": "Author-driven horizontal moving platform. The entity's `pos` and\n`width/height` define the platform's starting AABB; `sweep_dx`\ncontrols the horizontal travel range (positive sweeps right then\nping-pongs back, negative sweeps left first). `speed` is in\nworld px/s. The runtime overrides the legacy hardcoded sandbox\ntime-reference platform with the first authored MovingPlatform\nfound in the active LDtk area.\n",
			"width": 160,
